OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCovid: Boris Johnson makes 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Finquiry pledge to bereaved 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffamilies                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Boris Johnson has promised to appoint a
OL,6, chair for the official Covid inquiry   
OL,7, before Christmas, after meeting a      
OL,8, campaign group.                        
OL,10,FCovid-19 Bereaved Families for Justice 
OL,11,Fsaid he also pledged to involve them in
OL,12,Fthe decision, during a meeting with    
OL,13,Fthem in Downing Street.                
OL,15,FThe PM met the group earlier, having   
OL,16,Fdeclined to do so since last year.     
OL,18,FIt has been campaigning for a public   
OL,19,Finquiry into the pandemic, due to start
OL,20,Fin spring 2022, to begin immediately.  
